<h3>Mission</h3>

Prepare our students, through high quality internationally recognized instructional programs, to practice engineering professionally and ethically in a competitive global environment.

<h3>Vision</h3>

Provide our engineering graduates with the tools, skills and competencies necessary to understand and apply today's technologies and become leaders in developing and deploying tomorrow's technologies.

<h3>Program Educational Objective</h3>


To develop technically competent engineers well trained in basic principles so that they are able to identify and adapt to technological advancement.

To produce ethically & socially responsible and technically skilled engineers who are looked for by industries to provide engineering solution

To achieve position of increased technical and business responsibility within an organization

